La Chinec, ka sebopeho se selelele People's Republic of China (kapa People's Republic of China e nang le majusculed, PRC; Chinese e nolofalitsoeng: 中华人民共和国; Chinese Chinese: 中華人民共和國; pinyin: Zhōnghuá Rénmín Gònghéguó, pronounced / tʂʊŋ˥xua˧˥ ɻən˧˥mɪn˧˥kʊŋ˥˩xə˧˥kuɔ˧˥ / Mamela), eo hape e bitsoang People's China, kapa China ea Bokomonisi, ke naha e Asia Bochabela. E na le baahi ba fetang limilione tse likete tse 1,4, kapa hoo e ka bang karolo ea botšelela ea baahi ba lefatše, ke naha e nang le baahi ba bangata ka ho fetisisa lefatšeng. E na le litoropo tse tšeletseng tse nang le baahi ba fetang limilione tse leshome: motse-moholo Beijing, Shanghai, Chongqing, Tianjin, Canton le Shenzhen, hammoho le litoropo tse fetang mashome a mararo tsa bonyane baahi ba limilione tse peli. Ka sebaka sa 9,600,000 km2 ho latela UN8 kapa 9,596,960 km2 ho latela The World Factbook9, China hape ke naha e kholo ka ho fetisisa Asia Bochabela le naha ea boraro kapa ea bone e kholo ka ho fetisisa lefatšeng ka sebaka10. Chaena e tloha mabopong a Leoatle la Pacific ho ea Pamirs le Tian Shans, le ho tloha Lehoatateng la Gobi ho ea Himalaya le leboea ho Hloahloa ea Indochinese.

China ke e 'ngoe ea litho tse hlano tse sa feleng tsa Lekhotla la Ts'ireletso la Machaba a Kopaneng (Rephabliki ea China ho fihlela ka 1971 ebe People's Republic of China ho tloha ka letsatsi leo). Ke morekisi ea kholo ka ho fetisisa lefatšeng mme o na le libetsa tsa nyutlelie, sesole se seholo ka ho fetesisa lefatšeng (ho latela matla a basebetsi) le tekanyetso ea bobeli ea sesole e kholo ka ho fetisisa. E busoa ke Mokha oa Makomonisi oa China ho tloha ka 1949, Chaena e amohetse "moruo oa 'maraka oa bochaba" moo bokhaphithaliste le taolo ea bohatelli ea lipolotiki li kopanang hammoho ka mokhoa o itseng. Molaotheo oa People's Republic of China o o hlalosa e le "naha ea bochaba ea puso e hatellang ea demokrasi, e etelletsoeng pele ke basebetsi mme e ipapisitse le selekane sa basebetsi le balemi". Selelekela sa Molaotheo se totobatsa karolo e etelletseng pele ea Mokha oa Makomonisi oa China mme se ntse se tsoela pele ho qotsa semmuso Marxism-Leninism e le mohopolo oa mmuso oa naha. Fumana lintho tsohle tsa setso tsa China ho sena [https://www.traditions-de-chine.com/ boutique chinoise].

China ke e 'ngoe ea tsoelo-pele ea khale ka ho fetisisa lefats'eng,' me ka linako tse ling e boleloa e le tsoelo-pele ea khale ka ho fetesisa12. E simolohile phuleng ea Noka e Tala ebe e namela ka boroa (ho hapa libaka tse ka boroa ho Yangzi Jiang ho tsoa lesikeng la Han), bophirima (liketelo tsa pele Asia Bohareng tlasa Han, katoloso ea nakoana ho fihlela 'Leoatleng la Caspian tlasa Tang. , ho haptjoa ha Xinjiang le Tibet tlasa Qing13) le ka leboea (lesika la Qing, la semanchu, le tlisitse Manchuria le Mongolia Chaena). Ho ea ka nalane ea eona, Chaena e arotsoe khafetsa ebe e kopantsoe hape; e hapiloe habeli ka ho felletseng ke basele (ke Mamongolia lekholong la leshome le metso e meraro la lilemo le ke Manchus lekholong la leshome le metso e supileng la lilemo), leha ba qetellang ba ile ba amohela moetlo le tsamaiso ea China ho busa mmuso. Lesika la borena la hoqetela, Qing (lesika la mantlha la Manchurian le busitseng naha ho tloha ka 1644), le ile la ba le nako ea ho putlama nakong ea keketseho ea bokoloniale ea linaha tsa Bophirima, ea etella naha pele ho hloloa ho fihlela e hloloa ke lintoa tsa opium. Puso ea borena ea China e ile ea lihuoa ke phetohelo ea China ea 1911 mme Rephabliki ea China ea phatlalatsoa ke Sun Yat-sen mathoasong a 1912. Ka 1927, ho ile ha qhoma ntoa ea lehae le Mokha oa Makomonisi oa China, o ileng oa sitisoa nakong ea ntoa le Japane ho fihlela Majapane a inehela ka 1945. Kamora tlholo ea sesole ea Mokha oa Makomonisi oa Chaena holim'a Kuomintang e ileng ea isoa botlamuoeng Taiwan le mmuso oa Rephabliki ea China, People's Republic of China e phatlalalitsoe ka la 1 Mphalane 1949 naheng ea China. E itlhahisa e le "repaboliki ea bokomonisi", 'me ho tloha 1997 e sebelisitse taolo liprofinseng tse mashome a mabeli a metso e' meli, libaka tse hlano tse ikemetseng, bomasepala ba bane (ho kenyeletsoa Beijing) le libaka tse peli tse ikhethileng tsa tsamaiso (Hong Kong le Macao).

China e bile le nako ea morao-rao ea Neolithic le Metal Ages ha e bapisoa le Anatolia le Mesopotamia, empa e ne e le setsi sa mahlale a mangata makaleng a mahlale le bonono9. Ke qalehong ea liqapi tse kholo tse kholo tse kang khampasi14, pampiri15, banknot16 kapa phofo e ntšo17. Tsoelo-pele ea China e aparetse Asia Bochabela kaofela, haholoholo ho tsa bolumeli (Confucianism, Taoism le nts'etsopele ea Buddhism ea Chan), lipuo (litlhaku tsa China li sebelisitsoe ho pholletsa le sebaka sena mme mantsoe a mangata a China a teng lipuong tse buuoang moo), Hape le bonono (ho ngola litšoantšo, ho penta, ho hatisa, liletsa tsa 'mino, bonono).
